OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying dry,
OL,6,Fbut with patchy low cloud spreading
OL,7,Finland from the coast. Some showers
OL,8,Fpossible in the early hours of
OL,9,FThursday, perhaps heavy and thundery
OL,10,Fat times.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FAny low cloud quickly
OL,13,Fclearing to leave a fine sunny day for
OL,14,Fthe most with the chance of some
OL,15,Fshowers afternoon, some of which could
OL,16,Fbe thundery. Temperatures increasing
OL,17,Fagain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
