OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDry but
OL,6,Fa little cooler on Friday. A band of
OL,7,Fpatchy rain moving in late on
OL,8,FSaturday, perhaps heavy and persistent
OL,9,Fovernight. Unsettled with showers
OL,10,Fpossible on Sunday.
